        <item>
            <title>【评测】vivo X200 Pro mini 国行开箱评测，机仔细细易外携 + 单手握机操控手感佳 + 高屏占比荧幕表现出色 + 相机夜摄较逊色 + 旗舰效能电量超长气</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/05/vivo-x200promini-chinaversion-review/review-2/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=vivo-x200promini-chinaversion-review</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/05/vivo-x200promini-chinaversion-review/review-2/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Edward]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 14:33:31 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提电话]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[评测]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[vivo]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[X200]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[X200 Pro mini]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1273011</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>早前笔者就已为大家评测过 vivo 刚推出的国行版本 X200 Pro，但其实同场发布有另一部笔者觉得更吸引的新机，就是属于机仔细细但同样是旗舰效能配置的 X200 Pro mini。究竟这部「细细粒」表现上是否可以媲美「大阿哥」X200 Pro？就让 Edward 为 unwire.hk 读者们来个详细开箱评测吧。</p><h2>vivo X200 Pro mini 开箱直击</h2><p>在为大家分享 vivo X200 Pro mini 的使用体验前，同样地先让 Edward 为大家来个开箱直击吧。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273084" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04639-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04639-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04639.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲这就是 vivo X200 Pro mini 的包装盒，大家可以见到它与「大哥」X200 Pro 的包装盒设计一模一样，不过明显比较细一点。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273085" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04641-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04641-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04641.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲笔者借测的是钛青版，配置为 16GB RAM + 512GB 内存。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273086" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04643-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04643-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04643.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲一打开包装盒，就已经见到 X200 Pro mini 的真身。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273087" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04644-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04644-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04644.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而底层就会见到所有 X200 Pro mini 附送的配件。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273088" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04646-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04646-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04646.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲大家可以见到 X200 Pro mini 除了附送透明手机壳外，亦设有 SIM 卡槽针、充电火牛及 USB-A to USB-C 数据电源线。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273089" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04650-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04650-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04650.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273090" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04651-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04651-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04651.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273091" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04654-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04654-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04654.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲最后撕走手机上的包装纸，再长按开关键，就可以开启手机电源并进行初设始定了，至此开箱部分完毕。</p><h2>设计与「大机」相若但细机更好揸手</h2><p>先说设计上吧，今次 vivo 推出的「细屏旗舰」X200 Pro mini，在机身设计上基本上与「大机」X200 Pro 有 8 成相似，机背同样采用加入磨砂工艺的玻璃物料，机边依然采用较厚身平面的边框，只是机面机底边位取走了弧位，改为采用直角设计，令 Pro mini 感觉上就像一部拥有四圆角的「砖头」。不过由于它的机身大细比「大机」细得多，体积只有「大机」的 84% 左右，厚度亦比旧机更薄，只有 8.15mm，重量更只有 187g，加上依然采用超幼边框及超高屏占比的荧幕，令「机仔细细」的 X200 Pro mini 不但外携时更加方便放入裤袋或褛袋，长时间单手握机拿在手上使用亦更加舒服，单手握机打字亦自然没有问题。而且它机身较细较薄较轻，在「大机」出现的头重尾轻问题在 X200 Pro mini 上似乎不太感觉得到，亦令使用手感比「大机」更理想。值得一提的是，虽然机身设计与「大机」相若，但 Pro mini 的配色，除了黑、白两个较大路的款式外，另外两款配色「钛青」及「微粉」就属于较具活力、较清新的配色，相对「大机」的「宝石蓝」及「钛色」，相信更能吸引后生仔入手。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273093" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04697-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04697-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04697.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲X200 Pro mini 在设计上，基本上与「大哥」X200 Pro 有 8 成相似，最大分别就是机身明显细了一个圈。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273100" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04675-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04675-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04675.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲究竟 X200 Pro mini 机身有几「细」？笔者拿来同样是细机旗舰的 iPhone 13 Pro 比一比，大家可以见到 X200 Pro mini 也只是比 iPhone 13 Pro 大一点点。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273096" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04679-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04679-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04679.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273097" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04668-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04668-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04668.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲另一个 X200 Pro mini 与 X200 Pro 最大的机身设计分别，就是前者采用的是机面机底边位均是全平的设计。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273098" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04665-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04665-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04665.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而机侧边框依然采用金属物料制造。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273099" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04662-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04662-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04662.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲至于机背，就依然用上加入了磨砂工艺的强化玻璃物料，而今次笔者借测的钛青色，确实十分耐看。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273106" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04702-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04702-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04702.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲至于机边，由于采用平面设计，加上机身不算大，所以握机时完全没有界手感。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273107" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04708-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04708-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04708.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273108" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04705-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04705-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04705.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273109" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04710-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04710-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04710.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲另外笔者以电子磅量度过，X200 Pro mini 机身重量只是 191.4g，以旗舰手机来说算是颇轻身，外携使用十分方便。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273101" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04700-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04700-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04700.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273102" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04699-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04699-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04699.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273103" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04701-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04701-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04701.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273104" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04703-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04703-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04703.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲由于机身细又薄，而且颇轻身，所以即使长时间单手握机操控或打字，手感依然十分舒服。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273110" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04676-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04676-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04676.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲另外，它同样内建了荧幕下指纹解锁功能，不过大家要留意的是，它只是一般的屏下指纹模组，而非像 X200 Pro 般采用超声波荧幕下指纹辨识技术，所以如果用家手指湿，在 X200 Pro mini 上是不能解锁的。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273111" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04666-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04666-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04666.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273112" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04667-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04667-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04667.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲至于机身配置方面，音量键及开关键设于机身右侧，而内置喇叭、USB-C 插槽及 SIM 卡槽就位于机底。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1273113 alignnone" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241103_-13-267x580.jpg" alt="" width="267" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241103_-13-267x580.jpg 267w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241103_-13.jpg 414w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 267px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1273114 alignnone" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241103_-14-267x580.jpg" alt="" width="267" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241103_-14-267x580.jpg 267w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241103_-14.jpg 414w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 267px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1273115 alignnone" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241103_-15-267x580.jpg" alt="" width="267" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241103_-15-267x580.jpg 267w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241103_-15.jpg 414w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 267px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1273116 alignnone" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241103_-16-267x580.jpg" alt="" width="267" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241103_-16-267x580.jpg 267w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241103_-16.jpg 414w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 267px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲介面方面，X200 Pro mini 内建了 OriginOS 5，设计上与其他采用相同 OS 的 vivo 国行手机相比如出一辙。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1273117 alignnone" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241101_-2-267x580.jpg" alt="" width="267" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241101_-2-267x580.jpg 267w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241101_-2.jpg 414w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 267px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1273118 alignnone" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241103_-17-267x580.jpg" alt="" width="267" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241103_-17-267x580.jpg 267w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot_20241103_-17.jpg 414w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 267px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲X200 Pro mini 国行同样内建了 Google 框架，所以只需要在官方商店下载并安装 Google Play Store，登入后就可如港行般下载及安装软件或游戏。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273119" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04714-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04714-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04714.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273120" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04715-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04715-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04715.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲笔者实测过可以完美使用 Google Play Store 之余，亦可安装及使用各种 GMS 服务。</p><br /><b>
]]>
